description: Under normal circumstances, at least 95% of the fund's total assets (exclusive of collateral held from securities lending) will be invested in component securities of the index and investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the economic characteristics of such component securities. The index is a fundamentally weighted index that is comprised of high dividend-yielding international common stocks outside the financial sector. The fund is non-diversified.
name: WisdomTree International Dividend ex-Financials Fund
